<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Dolphin House Beach Resort">

  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto py-12 px-6">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-center text-gray-800 mb-8">
      Privacy Policy
    </h1>

    <p class="text-gray-600 text-center mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      This Privacy Policy describes how <strong>Dolphin House Beach Resort</strong> collects, uses, and protects your personal information when you visit our website or make a booking with us.
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-sky-700 mb-2">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, and booking details submitted via our booking form or contact form.</li>
          <li><strong>Payment Information:</strong> We may collect limited payment-related information to confirm bookings (handled securely via payment gateways).</li>
          <li><strong>Automatically Collected Data:</strong> IP address, browser type, and pages visited â€” collected through Google Analytics and cookies to improve user experience.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-sky-700 mb-2">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2">

          <li>To respond to inquiries or service requests submitted via our website or WhatsApp.</li>
          <li>To send booking confirmations, reminders, or updates related to your stay.</li>
          <li>To improve our website, marketing, and customer service quality.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-sky-700 mb-2">3. Data Protection & Security</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2">
          <li>We use secure hosting (HTTPS) and Cloudflare protection to safeguard all personal data.</li>
          <li>Your information is never sold or shared with unauthorized third parties.</li>
          <li>Only authorized staff have access to booking data stored in our secure database (Cloudflare D1).</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-sky-700 mb-2">4. Cookies</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Our website may use cookies to enhance browsing experience and collect analytics data.</li>
          <li>You can choose to disable cookies in your browser settings at any time.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-sky-700 mb-2">5. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2">
          <li>These services may collect anonymous usage data per their respective privacy policies.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-sky-700 mb-2">6. Your Rights</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2">
          <li>You can request to view, modify, or delete your personal data by contacting us directly.</li>
          <li>To withdraw consent or unsubscribe from any communication, email us at <a href="mailto:privacy@dolphinhouse-alibaug.com" class="text-sky-600 hover:underline">privacy@dolphinhouse-alibaug.com</a>.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-sky-700 mb-2">7. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3">
          <strong>Dolphin House Beach Resort</strong><br/>
